Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Star Compass: a mysterious instrument\Nthat always points to the far reaches of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Its needle led not to the far end of the sky above,\Nbut in fact to the exact opposite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the very depths of this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It pointed to the far reaches of the Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It had already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of this Star Compass was most beautifully\Nrevealed, and from the depths of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a mysterious robot boy appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't mark the beginning, then what does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When cave raiding in the Abyss,\Nthe return journey presents a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The deeper you go, the greater and more severe\Nthe physical toll of heading home becomes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning from the depths' first layer,\Nyou experience mild dizziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From the second layer:\Nnausea, headaches, and numbness of the extremities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From the fourth layer:\Nintense pain throughout the body and bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sixth layer and beyond:\Nthe loss of your humanity or even death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This mysterious phenomenon,\Nwhich is unavoidable for any human cave raider...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is called the Curse of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,robots should be unaffected by the curse, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you must've come from the bottom\Nof the Abyss, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming that's true,\Nthen what did I come up here to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The Compilation of Recorded Relics!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Recorded Relics"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a field guide to the major Relics\Nthat have been unearthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Unheard Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Classified as a special-grade Relic,\Nit's a "bell that stops time"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Reg! My mother was the one who found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I searched everywhere inside this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing listed that's anything like Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, care to fill us in on what you've found out\Nabout Reg's features?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He puzzlingly can run on either food or electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and on top of possessing a strange power\Nthat can melt petrified trees in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he has skin that's smooth\Ndespite being able to stop a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And even fire was unable to burn his hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems his vision and hearing is better than mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, his arm can extend about 40 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His metal-looking parts are made of\Nsome mysterious flexible material,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which I couldn't pierce even with a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A drill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He also has a belly button,\Nbut I couldn't really see inside his butthole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to probe him with a measuring stick,\Nbut it broke while inside him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, his penis doesn't appear to be mechanical\Nbut more like a real one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Riko, that's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We couldn't stop her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Penis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the stick out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving aside the second half of the report,\Nnone of those features are listed within the Relic record...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if they were,\Nthey'd be classified above even grade-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg's body is a bundle of special-grade Relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the whole history of the Abyss,\Nhe is perhaps one of the most valuable Relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a so-called Aubade -\Na supreme treasure of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's super awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my mother found one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg will be quickly taken away,\Nhis existence will be concealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and he may even be dismantled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, our usual classes\Nand jobs start up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we won't be able to stay with him\Nall the time then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll keep him hidden in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Even your dog was found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it the "Bring Together Leader and Reg Strategy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to be a cave raider?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no family. My big sister died, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that if I work here, I can become a cave raider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you were born in Orth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister found me a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything before that\Ndue to an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I began rag-picking with her in a\Ncliff-side neighborhood in Orth's south district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that backstory's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it is, right?\NI doubt that Leader's ever been to the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,been like this for the full year I've had my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man in the cliff-side neighborhood\Nsaid it's foreign technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Clench it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems your grip is strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... It's Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He pulled it off...\NAlright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is an Aubade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know anything about the incident\Nin the Depths of the Abyss the other day, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It went well, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, I became a student at Belchero Orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and set my sights on becoming a cave raider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hammerbeak chicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that huge thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It swallowed up that hammerbeak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the hammerbeaks are fighting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bite 'em! Bite 'em good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you don't lose interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get bored of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, this huge one... Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did Uncle Habo's letter say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he says that he's about to head\Nto the second layer's Inverted Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Inverted Forest is pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The trees, grass, and everything else\Ngrows upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And fog rises up from the sea of clouds directly below.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like some kind of inverted waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost sound like you've seen it firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming to be a White Whistle too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo wants to become one, too,\Neven though he's not young anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is being one really all that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Laffi, do you have the stuff on this list?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... uh, I need to go grab a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've got the others down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're pretty quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You done making deliveries?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I hear Habo is aspiring to be a White Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I really admire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, our country celebrates them as heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,White Whistles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But admiring them isn't exactly the same as\Nwanting to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, why? They don't have any depth limit, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're truly the best of the best among us cave raiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the day I'm made a White Whistle,\NI'll go all out to give birth to a ton of legends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys have jobs to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months had passed before I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised by how well I'm fitting in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's three more days until I go on my first cave-raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which also means saying goodbye to this bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably won't be getting any bigger,\Nbut you'll keep on growing and growing, Kiyui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Word is Habo's squad is returning home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go greet them at the grand pier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyui, it's dangerous there, so you stay behind, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Habo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a whistle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A white whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! A white whistle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I figured out whose whistle that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lyza's! "Lyza the Annihilator"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's Lyza's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza the Annihilator's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Annihilator"... What an unsettling name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!\N"Annihilator"... What an unsettling name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Annihilator"... What an unsettling name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why just her whistle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's only remaining unexplored chasm,\Nthe great devilish pit, Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is we, the cave raiders, who dare challenge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The apprentice Red Whistles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The proficient Blue Whistles!\NThe assistant-instructor Moon Whistles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The expert Black Whistles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally... those who stand atop them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the masters who have surpassed\Ntheir human limitations to challenge the Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the White Whistles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They have brought us numerous discoveries\Nthat changed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how very deep they go,\Nthey remain our brilliantly shining nether stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the soul of the one who stood out\Nas the greatest even among the White Whistles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,has at last returned home after more than 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Her last dive has come to its completion right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She slayed countless dangerous creatures\Nthat rose from the depths!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your replicas of the Annihilator's white whistle here!\NShe slayed countless dangerous creatures\Nthat rose from the depths!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve times foreign cave raiders attacked,\Nand every single time she turned the tables on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Time for the big gem projector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People call her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza the Annihilator!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to purchase a copy of the Annihilator's biography\Nor a replica of her white whistle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,be sure to visit Belchero Orphanage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And please be wary of imitations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... really okay for me to keep this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike other whistles,\Nthat one can only be used by its original owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... that's not really what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there someone more worthy of it than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's customary for a relative to be the one\Nto receive a white whistle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be fine with you taking it. Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's too heavy a responsibility to bear,\Nyou can always entrust it to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, Lyza had also been carrying\Na sealed document.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We received both it and that white whistle\Nfrom a sentry at the Seeker Camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, right now it's being examined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So it might take some time to get to you, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying it's a letter... from my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I suppose it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, I'm sure it's a letter addressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing sitting around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Resurrection Festival is meant to show\Njust how great your mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very important day for you, too.\NMake sure to really take it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Lyza loved festivals,\Nand in a way this is her final one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother was your instructor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being one of the White Whistles\NI look up to so much, I can't even remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not exactly sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like someone I aspired to be\Njust suddenly disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lyza went in for her last dive,\Nyou were still just 2 years old, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a cave raider, she was every bit\Nthe legendary White Whistle people say she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That said... I hardly even got the chance\Nto go cave raiding with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What I know of her is from her time here on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a heavy drinker, quick to get into fights,\Nand you could never tell how honest she was being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she had a horribly unbalanced diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wasn't a White Whistle,\Nshe would have been just another weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a real mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How are your eyes doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, they're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm wearing my glasses,\NI don't get headaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the issue with your eyes\Nis different than common "bad eyesight."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your vision itself is fine and free from abnormalities...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but you suffer headaches unless\Nyou view everything through crystal lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The symptoms may be mysterious,\Nbut their cause is quite clear:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Curse of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad eyesight isn't from always staying up late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was nonsense we made up to teach you discipline...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been 12 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was a bit before that actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother Lyza had just become pregnant with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when she had to go down to the fourth layer\Nwith a survey team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a special mission ordered\Nby the country's powers that be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She was to retrieve the Unheard Bell, a special-grade\NRelic that had been discovered in the depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Their cave raiding proved arduous\Nand stretched on for over 10 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They had repeated run-ins with foreign cave raiders,\Nand the survey team was nearly wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at that time your father,\Na Black Whistle named Torka, lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the midst of it all, you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Depths of the Abyss... is where you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,um... so does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strong against the Curse of the Abyss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget about how much you were throwing up\Nyour first time cave raiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascending from the fourth layer\Nis something that's unbearable even for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So, why am I still alive, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the Curse-Repelling Vessel\Nthat Lyza took along with her to thank for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it was dreadfully heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the now-decimated team\Nno longer had the strength to carry it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, it seems I'm not actually alive, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza abandoned the Unheard Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving behind the corpses of their comrades,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,she carried you together\Nwith a still-standing squad member.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing home just one special-grade Relic\Nis enough to enrich the city and ensure a squad's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet Lyza chose you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prestige and riches, her comrades and their trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She desired to have you so much\Nthat she was willing to give that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she made use of a Relic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the Curse of the Abyss\Ncould still not be fully warded off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza lamented that she was unable to protect your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You grew up extremely healthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:19:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the face of the pressure of having a mother of\Nsuch stature, you're trying to choose your own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, the one she risked her life to protect\Nis still going strong to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this life the legendary White Whistle\NLyza the Annihilator left you with...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza settled the score with the foreign country\Nthat caused her trouble and then recovered the Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some things are better left unsaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Abyss, I'm comin' for ya. I'm goin' down there, Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a White Whistle in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think Riko's been actin'\Na bit strange lately?\NI'll be a White Whistle in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's oddly cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's forcing herself to act cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's forcing herself to act cheerful...\NAbyss, I'm comin' for ya. I'm goin' down there, Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother is missing in action, after all.\NAbyss, I'm comin' for ya. I'm goin' down there, Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother is missing in action, after all.\NI'll be a White Whistle in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a White Whistle in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I doubt she has such a\Ncomplex personality, seriously now...\NI'll be a White Whistle in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I doubt she has such a\Ncomplex personality, seriously now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey now, Reg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've received permission to view the sealed document.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be at headquarters by 18:00. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you go with her. She might behave erratically\Nand I can't stand watching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just up ahead. I'll accompany you as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from touching anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother went down there 10 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet none of these are in the field guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen any of these before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Riko? The letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some parts are different here and there,\Nbut this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, there's a piece of paper beside it with only writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a letter... it's pretty short.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, shine the light on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the netherworld's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting.
